jalse.attributes

Interface AttributeContainerListener<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Attribute type to trigger for.

    public interface AttributeContainerListener<T>
    Listener for AttributeType value manipulation. When attributes are added, updated or removed the suitable defined method will be triggered. A change is a manual fire of the trigger to denote a internal state change of the attribute. Unique AttributeContainerEvent will be supplied for each trigger.
    See Also:
    AttributeContainer, DefaultAttributeContainer
